[1] Worldwide 2009 update
Date: Wed, 2 Sep 2009
Source: FAOAIDEnews Animal Influenza Disease Emergency Situation
Update No 61, 31 Aug 2009 [edited]


H5N1 AI occurrence during 2009
-----------------------------
Note: This list has been compiled on the basis of information up to
31 Aug 2009.

August: Egypt, Mongolia
July: Indonesia
June: Bangladesh, Russian Federation, Viet Nam
May: China, India
April: China (Hong Kong)
March: Germany
February: Lao PDR, Nepal

